<A NAME="ref-chapter-meshsimplification"></A><h1>Triangulated Surface Mesh Simplification <BR>
<I>Reference&nbsp;Manual</I></h1>
<P>

This chapter introduces the concepts and classes of the triangulated surface mesh simplification package.<BR>

The packages provides a policy-based algorithm for the simplification of triangulated surface meshes
by iterative edge-collapsing.
<P>

